   * A fairly LSB compliant GNU/Linux distribution.  (1)

   * Linux 2.4 or 2.6 kernel (2.4.10 - 2.4.27) or (2.6.3 - 2.6.15)

   * glibc2 or better.

   * GNU info (for info files).

   * GNU groff (for man pages).  (2)

   * OpenSS7 Linux Fast-STREAMS (streams-0.7a.5
     (http://www.openss7.org/tarballs/streams-0.7a.5.tar.bz2) or better) (3)

   * OpenSS7 STREAMS Compatibility Modules (strcompat-0.9.2.3
     (http://www.openss7.org/tarballs/strcompat-0.9.2.3.tar.bz2) or better)

If you need to rebuild the package from sources with modifications, you will
need a larger GNU toolchain as described in *Note Downloading from CVS::.

